msgstr "Responses APIを使用"

msgid ""
"Required to surface reasoning content on OpenAI / Poe / OpenRouter / Azure "
"(POSTs to /v1/responses instead of /v1/chat/completions). Auto-set when "
"picking a preset."
msgstr ""
"OpenAI / Poe / OpenRouter / Azureで推論コンテンツを表示するために必要です（/"
"v1/chat/completionsの代わりに/v1/responsesにPOSTします）。プリセット選択時に"
